ion/externalaccessory/eawifiunconfiguredaccessory) object."},{"t":"EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryConfigurationStatus.failed","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryConfigurationStatus/failed","r":"Case","a":"The configuration failed."},{"t":"EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryConfigurationStatus.success","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryConfigurationStatus/success","r":"Case","a":"The configuration of the accessory succeeded."},{"t":"EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryConfigurationStatus.userCancelledConfiguration","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryConfigurationStatus/userCancelledConfiguration","r":"Case","a":"The user cancelled the configuration process."},{"t":"EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryProperties","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryProperties","r":"Structure","a":"Options that can be combined using the C bitwise `OR` operator to represent the properties of an unconfigured accessory."},{"t":"EA_EXTERN","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EA_EXTERN","r":"Macro"},{"t":"EA_EXTERN_CLASS","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EA_EXTERN_CLASS","r":"Macro"},{"t":"EA_EXTERN_CLASS_AVAILABLE","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EA_EXTERN_CLASS_AVAILABLE","r":"Macro"},{"t":"External Accessory","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory","r":"Framework","a":"Communicate with accessories that connect to a device with the Apple Lightning connector, or with Bluetooth wireless technology."},{"t":"Null Connection ID","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/null-connection-id","r":"API Collection","a":"The ID for an unconnected accessory."},{"t":"accessory","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EASession/accessory","r":"Instance Property","a":"The accessory attached to the session."},{"t":"accessory","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryManager/AccessoryDidDisconnectMessage/accessory","r":"Instance Property"},{"t":"accessory","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryManager/AccessoryDidConnectMessage/accessory","r":"Instance Property"},{"t":"accessoryBrowser(_:didFindUnconfiguredAccessories:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowserDelegate/accessoryBrowser(_:didFindUnconfiguredAccessories:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Indicates that the browser found a new unconfigured accessory that matches the filter predicate defined at the start of the search."},{"t":"accessoryBrowser(_:didFinishConfiguringAccessory:with:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowserDelegate/accessoryBrowser(_:didFinishConfiguringAccessory:with:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Indicates that the browser has completed configuring the specified accessory."},{"t":"accessoryBrowser(_:didRemoveUnconfiguredAccessories:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowserDelegate/accessoryBrowser(_:didRemoveUnconfiguredAccessories:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Indicates that the browser removed an unconfigured accessory from the search results."},{"t":"accessoryBrowser(_:didUpdate:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowserDelegate/accessoryBrowser(_:didUpdate:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Indicates that the browser\u2019s state has changed."},{"t":"accessoryDidDisconnect(_:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryDelegate/accessoryDidDisconnect(_:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Tells the delegate that the specified accessory was disconnected from the device."},{"t":"alreadyConnected","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EABluetoothAccessoryPickerError/alreadyConnected","r":"Type Property"},{"t":"configureAccessory(_:withConfigurationUIOn:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowser/configureAccessory(_:withConfigurationUIOn:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Begins the configuration process for the specified accessory."},{"t":"connectedAccessories","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryManager/connectedAccessories","r":"Instance Property","a":"The accessory objects corresponding to the list of currently connected accessories."},{"t":"connectionID","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessory/connectionID","r":"Instance Property","a":"The accessory\u2019s unique ID for connecting to the iOS-based device."},{"t":"delegate","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowser/delegate","r":"Instance Property","a":"The object that acts as the delegate of the browser and receives browser events."},{"t":"delegate","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessory/delegate","r":"Instance Property","a":"The object that acts as the delegate of the accessory."},{"t":"dockType","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessory/dockType","r":"Instance Property"},{"t":"errorDomain","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EABluetoothAccessoryPickerError/errorDomain","r":"Type Property"},{"t":"firmwareRevision","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessory/firmwareRevision","r":"Instance Property","a":"The current firmware version for the accessory."},{"t":"hardwareRevision","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessory/hardwareRevision","r":"Instance Property","a":"The hardware version of the accessory."},{"t":"init(accessory:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryManager/AccessoryDidDisconnectMessage/init(accessory:)","r":"Initializer"},{"t":"init(accessory:forProtocol:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EASession/init(accessory:forProtocol:)","r":"Initializer","a":"Initializes the session for the specified accessory and protocol."},{"t":"init(accessory:userSelected:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryManager/AccessoryDidConnectMessage/init(accessory:userSelected:)","r":"Initializer"},{"t":"init(delegate:queue:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowser/init(delegate:queue:)","r":"Initializer","a":"Creates a browser object that scans for unconfigured accessories."},{"t":"init(rawValue:)","p":"documentation/Exter