e serial number of the accessory."},{"t":"shared()","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryManager/shared()","r":"Type Method","a":"Returns the shared accessory manager object for the iOS-based device."},{"t":"showBluetoothAccessoryPicker(withNameFilter:completion:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryManager/showBluetoothAccessoryPicker(withNameFilter:completion:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Displays an alert that allows the user to pair the device with a Bluetooth accessory."},{"t":"ssid","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessory/ssid","r":"Instance Property","a":"The Wi-Fi SSID of the accessory."},{"t":"startSearchingForUnconfiguredAccessories(matching:)","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowser/startSearchingForUnconfiguredAccessories(matching:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Starts the search for unconfigured accessories that match the specified predicate."},{"t":"stopSearchingForUnconfiguredAccessories()","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowser/stopSearchingForUnconfiguredAccessories()","r":"Instance Method","a":"Stops the search for unconfigured accessories."},{"t":"unconfiguredAccessories","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowser/unconfiguredAccessories","r":"Instance Property","a":"The set of unconfigured accessories that have been discovered."},{"t":"unregisterForLocalNotifications()","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryManager/unregisterForLocalNotifications()","r":"Instance Method","a":"Stops the delivery of accessory-related notifications to the current application."},{"t":"userSelected","p":"documentation/ExternalAccessory/EAAccessoryManager/AccessoryDidConnectMessage/userSelected","r":"Instance Property"}]